  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK364">
<l>tūuymai yeṉpa tavāviṉmai maṟṟatu</l>
<l> vāaymai vēṇṭa varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Purity (of mind) consists in freedom from desire and that (freedom from desire) is the fruit of the love of truth.</l>
            </lg>
